com.example.taskmagic

Class UserTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.taskmagic.UserTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UserTask
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Created by Yipu on 21/02/2018. UserTask represents an task object. Each task can have one of the four states (requested, bidded, assigned, DONE) They are used to organized any user activity
